  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>DEMO version released for Your FEEDBACK to make the game BETTER.</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Very STRANGE and UNIQUE Indie Rage PSX Styled Retro Horror Game...</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>STORY</strong></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>You came to Nolemland for adventure, but now you're Chuck’s slave, trapped in a nightmare. His son’s hunger never ends, and neither does your job - unless you find the one way to break the cycle and destroy Chuck’s world.</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >This is CHUCK:</h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3565820/extras/8fb2c4570cb1723c029cb332d8e27dfb.poster.avif?t=1746023946\" width=564 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3565820/extras/8fb2c4570cb1723c029cb332d8e27dfb.webm?t=1746023946\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3565820/extras/8fb2c4570cb1723c029cb332d8e27dfb.mp4?t=1746023946\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >This is his STARVING SON:</h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3565820/extras/83784a54f46fc98247763ac895b2e2fa.poster.avif?t=1746023946\" width=566 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3565820/extras/83784a54f46fc98247763ac895b2e2fa.webm?t=1746023946\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3565820/extras/83784a54f46fc98247763ac895b2e2fa.mp4?t=1746023946\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>RANDOMLY GENERATED maze of wires vs. SINGLE WHEEL!</strong><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3565820/extras/c8c37c6e12ce7a688f94e1247c781a21.poster.avif?t=1746023946\" width=562 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3565820/extras/c8c37c6e12ce7a688f94e1247c781a21.webm?t=1746023946\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3565820/extras/c8c37c6e12ce7a688f94e1247c781a21.mp4?t=1746023946\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Find MELONS to FEED THE KID</strong><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3565820/extras/e16a43d9689fceb7a68c5da5e0bda2fb.poster.avif?t=1746023946\" width=560 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3565820/extras/e16a43d9689fceb7a68c5da5e0bda2fb.webm?t=1746023946\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3565820/extras/e16a43d9689fceb7a68c5da5e0bda2fb.mp4?t=1746023946\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>3 DIFFICULTIES:  </strong></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Noob,  Classic,  and  NIGHTMARE!</strong><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3565820/extras/9e1d9b331ab97dd0e2c30ba72b7afd21.poster.avif?t=1746023946\" width=562 height=448 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3565820/extras/9e1d9b331ab97dd0e2c30ba72b7afd21.webm?t=1746023946\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3565820/extras/9e1d9b331ab97dd0e2c30ba72b7afd21.mp4?t=1746023946\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>The FASTEST players will land on the LEADERBOARDS.</strong></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3565820/extras/c0738b7145192217795e6cd7582960e9.poster.avif?t=1746023946\" width=562 height=448 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3565820/extras/c0738b7145192217795e6cd7582960e9.webm?t=1746023946\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3565820/extras/c0738b7145192217795e6cd7582960e9.mp4?t=1746023946\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3565820/extras/2b784bf24e8b13563d08ded46dc5b25e.poster.avif?t=1746023946\" width=562 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3565820/extras/2b784bf24e8b13563d08ded46dc5b25e.webm?t=1746023946\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3565820/extras/2b784bf24e8b13563d08ded46dc5b25e.mp4?t=1746023946\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>- also if you get (un)lucky, you might find the SECRET MODE.</strong></h2>",
